item.title: Attend Daymunc
item.description: Attendance Information If you are interested in attending DAYMUNC XXIII, email the Secretary General at #{contact[“Secretary General”]}. DAYMUNC registration fee: Below are the following instructions by Sinclair Community College’s (SCC) Office of the Bursar on how payments are to be made: Sinclair requires payment of deposits or full delegate payments directly to the College Bursar’s office and John Coyle assists us with this process.
